      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems covering contact, large-deformation, and elastoplastic regimes must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Each solver in the ensemble has been verified against published ASME benchmark suites including contact patch tests and elastoplastic beam benchmarks. Results are within accepted tolerances."
    },
    {
