      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study must demonstrate < 5% change in quantities of interest between successive refinements.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh convergence study was conducted for each model in the ensemble. Peak von Mises stress and construct stiffness changed by less than 3.2% between the medium and fine meshes, meeting the acceptance criterion."
    },
