      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual norms and energy balance must be documented for each simulation run.",
      "rationale": "Force and moment residuals converged to below 1e-6 relative tolerance in all runs. Energy balance was checked post-solution; no spurious energy generation was detected. Achieved level exceeds required level."
    },
    {
